s with confidence and truncated body. (B) braid observe search AUDIT returns the 226 audit observations. (C) braid observe show <entity> shows full body, confidence, category, concept, tags, timestamp. (D) braid observe recent 10 shows the 10 most recent. (E) All output modes work (human, agent, json, tsv). (F) Existing braid observe TEXT creation is not broken."
